00:33:45.700 --> 00:33:46.570 align:middle line:10%
It's all free.

00:33:46.570 --> 00:33:47.403 align:middle line:10%
>>LISA: Fascinating.

00:33:47.403 --> 00:33:50.800 align:middle line:10%
And so what did you learn
about time around this?

00:33:50.800 --> 00:33:52.630 align:middle line:10%
>>MEREDITH: Well, you
know if you take it

00:33:52.630 --> 00:33:56.900 align:middle line:10%
into a more modern,
practical-- first of all,

00:33:56.900 --> 00:33:59.530 align:middle line:10%
everything took way more
time than science is even

00:33:59.530 --> 00:34:01.510 align:middle line:10%
beginning to understand.

00:34:01.510 --> 00:34:03.550 align:middle line:84%
These things take
vast periods of time.

00:34:03.550 --> 00:34:06.100 align:middle line:84%
And they've gotten
pretty good at certain

00:34:06.100 --> 00:34:09.010 align:middle line:84%
dating to peg certain
events and certain places.

00:34:09.010 --> 00:34:11.860 align:middle line:84%
And I think what's happening
around the last flood,

00:34:11.860 --> 00:34:13.449 align:middle line:84%
for example, is
really interesting,

00:34:13.449 --> 00:34:15.240 align:middle line:84%
because they're finding
a lot of evidence--

00:34:15.240 --> 00:34:18.830 align:middle line:84%
you know the Gobekli
Tepe story and so forth.

00:34:18.830 --> 00:34:22.210 align:middle line:84%
But in terms of the
development of something,

00:34:22.210 --> 00:34:23.745 align:middle line:84%
that takes massive
amount of time

00:34:23.745 --> 00:34:25.120 align:middle line:84%
and a massive
amount of patience.

00:34:25.120 --> 00:34:27.280 align:middle line:84%
And I think you're
talking about it

00:34:27.280 --> 00:34:30.321 align:middle line:84%
more in the common sense
of how we use time?

00:34:30.321 --> 00:34:31.820 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: A little
bit of both though.

00:34:31.820 --> 00:34:35.310 align:middle line:84%
Because time-- as you're
speaking with these beings

00:34:35.310 --> 00:34:37.770 align:middle line:84%
and the amount of time
you're speaking about,

00:34:37.770 --> 00:34:40.949 align:middle line:84%
it all can really truly
collapse, can't it?

00:34:40.949 --> 00:34:44.089 align:middle line:90%
I mean it's timeless.

00:34:44.089 --> 00:34:44.889 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: Yes.

00:34:44.889 --> 00:34:46.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And this is
one of the things

00:34:46.430 --> 00:34:49.080 align:middle line:84%
that I haven't shared with
you, my near-death experience.

00:34:49.080 --> 00:34:50.580 align:middle line:84%
And that is one of
the things that I

00:34:50.580 --> 00:34:54.929 align:middle line:84%
saw was this timelessness
and this expanded

00:34:54.929 --> 00:34:56.401 align:middle line:90%
oneness of everything.

00:34:56.401 --> 00:34:57.650 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: Right, absolutely.

00:34:57.650 --> 00:34:59.816 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And that sense of
what you're talking about.

00:34:59.816 --> 00:35:00.630 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: Yes.

00:35:00.630 --> 00:35:04.920 align:middle line:84%
It was-- when you're looking
at life on that scale.

00:35:04.920 --> 00:35:07.060 align:middle line:84%
And you're looking at
intelligence on that scale--

00:35:07.060 --> 00:35:07.860 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:35:07.860 --> 00:35:12.720 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: --the one thing it
has in its favor is patience.

00:35:12.720 --> 00:35:15.204 align:middle line:90%
Patience take strength--

00:35:15.204 --> 00:35:16.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah, it does.

00:35:16.120 --> 00:35:17.170 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: --to
allow everything

00:35:17.170 --> 00:35:18.310 align:middle line:90%
to form in its own time.

00:35:18.310 --> 00:35:20.110 align:middle line:84%
And this is right
down to every time--

00:35:20.110 --> 00:35:21.700 align:middle line:90%
a watched pot never boils.

00:35:21.700 --> 00:35:24.400 align:middle line:84%
This comes down to making
a soup and so forth.

00:35:24.400 --> 00:35:27.040 align:middle line:84%
Which kind of gets us into you
were talking about the things I

00:35:27.040 --> 00:35:28.540 align:middle line:84%
share with people
in these workshops

00:35:28.540 --> 00:35:30.090 align:middle line:90%
and the experiences they have.

00:35:30.090 --> 00:35:33.040 align:middle line:84%
This is a big one, the
notion that now we're here--

00:35:33.040 --> 00:35:33.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes, right?

00:35:33.840 --> 00:35:35.140 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: We're part animal.

00:35:35.140 --> 00:35:39.040 align:middle line:84%
We're part splendidly
intelligent, creative, divine

00:35:39.040 --> 00:35:40.450 align:middle line:90%
aspect of ourselves.

00:35:40.450 --> 00:35:41.530 align:middle line:90%
It's there all the time.

00:35:41.530 --> 00:35:43.180 align:middle line:90%
That's who we are.

00:35:43.180 --> 00:35:44.890 align:middle line:90%
It's in our cells.

00:35:44.890 --> 00:35:47.050 align:middle line:90%
And we just don't access it.

00:35:47.050 --> 00:35:49.750 align:middle line:84%
We tend not to access it,
because Earth life blows it

00:35:49.750 --> 00:35:50.550 align:middle line:90%
out.

00:35:50.550 --> 00:35:53.660 align:middle line:84%
And now with social media
and all the distractions

00:35:53.660 --> 00:35:56.110 align:middle line:84%
we're not paying any
attention to the voice that's

00:35:56.110 --> 00:35:58.020 align:middle line:90%
constantly whispering to them.

00:35:58.020 --> 00:35:59.140 align:middle line:90%
They don't even hear it.

00:35:59.140 --> 00:36:00.970 align:middle line:90%
It's drowned out by the mundane.

00:36:00.970 --> 00:36:03.970 align:middle line:84%
So I help people open up and
listen to that voice again.

00:36:03.970 --> 00:36:04.770 align:middle line:90%
So they can--

00:36:04.770 --> 00:36:05.845 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: By slowing down?

00:36:05.845 --> 00:36:06.420 align:middle line:90%
By being quiet?

00:36:06.420 --> 00:36:08.260 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: Well, I
do a lot of exercises.

00:36:08.260 --> 00:36:10.930 align:middle line:84%
Like I said, even I even do
past life regressions with them

00:36:10.930 --> 00:36:14.440 align:middle line:84%
in groups and take them into
very specific meditations

00:36:14.440 --> 00:36:18.850 align:middle line:84%
of recovery of this skill,
this talent, these memories,

00:36:18.850 --> 00:36:19.690 align:middle line:90%
and such.

00:36:19.690 --> 00:36:24.190 align:middle line:84%
But time is-- that's
the interesting thing.

00:36:24.190 --> 00:36:27.040 align:middle line:84%
Because on Earth, people
get so frustrated and angry

00:36:27.040 --> 00:36:28.240 align:middle line:90%
and defeated.

00:36:28.240 --> 00:36:31.720 align:middle line:84%
And it almost always
is tied to time.

00:36:31.720 --> 00:36:33.490 align:middle line:84%
Because remember, if
you're a being that

00:36:33.490 --> 00:36:35.080 align:middle line:84%
can manifest at the
speed of thought

00:36:35.080 --> 00:36:38.650 align:middle line:84%
and you're now in this body in
this dimension in this material

00:36:38.650 --> 00:36:42.170 align:middle line:84%
world trying to manifest
something, it can take forever.

00:36:42.170 --> 00:36:44.120 align:middle line:90%
It can not happen at all.

00:36:44.120 --> 00:36:46.900 align:middle line:84%
So people become--
they live in despair.

00:36:46.900 --> 00:36:49.150 align:middle line:84%
When am I going to
have the love I want?

00:36:49.150 --> 00:36:50.550 align:middle line:90%
When am I going to have a baby?

00:36:50.550 --> 00:36:53.794 align:middle line:84%
When am I going to be able to
manifest the career I want?

00:36:53.794 --> 00:36:55.960 align:middle line:84%
Well, you've got to have a
buy in from a whole bunch

00:36:55.960 --> 00:36:57.070 align:middle line:90%
of other people--

00:36:57.070 --> 00:36:59.270 align:middle line:84%
or at least one other person
in the case of a baby--

00:36:59.270 --> 00:36:59.960 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:36:59.960 --> 00:37:01.418 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: --and
the entity that's

00:37:01.418 --> 00:37:04.490 align:middle line:84%
going to be born, two other
entities, just to have a baby.

00:37:04.490 --> 00:37:05.290 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:37:05.290 --> 00:37:07.539 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: The timing has
to be right for the one who

00:37:07.539 --> 00:37:11.050 align:middle line:84%
wants to come through, for
the father, for the bodies,

00:37:11.050 --> 00:37:11.920 align:middle line:90%
and everything.

00:37:11.920 --> 00:37:14.860 align:middle line:84%
So time becomes almost
we don't recognize

00:37:14.860 --> 00:37:17.260 align:middle line:90%
that the problem is just time.

00:37:17.260 --> 00:37:19.822 align:middle line:84%
Whereas, if you have
a sense of grace,

00:37:19.822 --> 00:37:22.030 align:middle line:84%
and you're listening to the
spirit and they're saying

00:37:22.030 --> 00:37:23.800 align:middle line:90%
you haven't met that one yet.

00:37:23.800 --> 00:37:25.540 align:middle line:90%
That's not here yet.

00:37:25.540 --> 00:37:26.890 align:middle line:90%
So enjoy what you're doing.

00:37:26.890 --> 00:37:28.690 align:middle line:84%
Learn from this
current experience.

00:37:28.690 --> 00:37:31.530 align:middle line:84%
But this isn't the one that
you'll have your child with.

00:37:31.530 --> 00:37:34.150 align:middle line:84%
If you can hear
yourself, you don't

00:37:34.150 --> 00:37:37.120 align:middle line:84%
get so wound up and
defeated and frustrated

00:37:37.120 --> 00:37:39.640 align:middle line:90%
and feel so hopeless over life.

00:37:39.640 --> 00:37:41.680 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's such an
interesting concept, time,

00:37:41.680 --> 00:37:44.620 align:middle line:84%
because sometimes it
feels like it blows by.

00:37:44.620 --> 00:37:48.400 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes it feels
like it is going so slowly.

00:37:48.400 --> 00:37:50.985 align:middle line:84%
So it begs the question
of what is time?

00:37:50.985 --> 00:37:51.785 align:middle line:90%
And--

00:37:51.785 --> 00:37:52.840 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: Well,
it's a construct here

00:37:52.840 --> 00:37:54.019 align:middle line:90%
that we're tied to.

00:37:54.019 --> 00:37:55.935 align:middle line:84%
You know, we've got
clocks running, every kind

00:37:55.935 --> 00:37:57.410 align:middle line:90%
of clock running all the time.

00:37:57.410 --> 00:38:01.245 align:middle line:84%
So in this dimension, we're tied
to our notion of linear time.

00:38:01.245 --> 00:38:02.620 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But in
other dimensions--

00:38:02.620 --> 00:38:02.920 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: You're not.

00:38:02.920 --> 00:38:04.720 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --or other
forms you're not.

00:38:04.720 --> 00:38:04.980 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: No.

00:38:04.980 --> 00:38:06.550 align:middle line:84%
That's why guides--
go back to guides.

00:38:06.550 --> 00:38:07.200 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:38:07.200 --> 00:38:09.575 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: A guide can tell
you this is going to happen.

00:38:09.575 --> 00:38:11.540 align:middle line:84%
You're like, oh,
yippee, I'm so excited.

00:38:11.540 --> 00:38:13.360 align:middle line:90%
My true love is on his way.

00:38:13.360 --> 00:38:15.160 align:middle line:84%
And then it's like
five years later.

00:38:15.160 --> 00:38:17.110 align:middle line:84%
And they said, well,
we didn't say when,

00:38:17.110 --> 00:38:19.840 align:middle line:90%
because they don't work in time.

00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:21.010 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: But we can.

00:38:21.010 --> 00:38:24.670 align:middle line:84%
I would say that you
have this incredible use

00:38:24.670 --> 00:38:26.980 align:middle line:84%
of this construct
of time to create

00:38:26.980 --> 00:38:29.980 align:middle line:84%
and creativity, and your
knowledge of the universe,

00:38:29.980 --> 00:38:32.410 align:middle line:84%
and your knowledge of
this wonderful star

00:38:32.410 --> 00:38:35.830 align:middle line:84%
system and guides, that
you intentionally manifest

00:38:35.830 --> 00:38:37.917 align:middle line:90%
your next steps, Regina.

00:38:37.917 --> 00:38:40.250 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: Well, I do, but
I just do it through desire.

00:38:40.250 --> 00:38:41.051 align:middle line:90%
It's what I want.

00:38:41.051 --> 00:38:42.258 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It's a great example.

00:38:42.258 --> 00:38:44.400 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: And so I don't
do it because someone

00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:46.300 align:middle line:90%
is telling me to do it.

00:38:46.300 --> 00:38:47.830 align:middle line:90%
I know-- well, it's my Dharma.

00:38:47.830 --> 00:38:49.700 align:middle line:84%
And I have known
that for a long time.

00:38:49.700 --> 00:38:50.500 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:38:50.500 --> 00:38:52.291 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: And I did
not want to be on TV.

00:38:52.291 --> 00:38:53.980 align:middle line:84%
I did not want to
be a news anchor.

00:38:53.980 --> 00:38:55.780 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to be
any of those things.

00:38:55.780 --> 00:38:57.700 align:middle line:84%
I just did it because
I was dared into it

00:38:57.700 --> 00:39:01.180 align:middle line:84%
and they kept offering me
jobs and I needed the money.

00:39:01.180 --> 00:39:04.570 align:middle line:84%
On a soul level, it was
training, training, training.

00:39:04.570 --> 00:39:06.340 align:middle line:90%
I just kept my nose in it.

00:39:06.340 --> 00:39:07.930 align:middle line:84%
Keep training,
because the time will

00:39:07.930 --> 00:39:10.700 align:middle line:84%
come when you have the freedom
to express it the way you wish.

00:39:10.700 --> 00:39:11.800 align:middle line:90%
And that's what happened.

00:39:11.800 --> 00:39:14.900 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That-- that's when
that all comes together.

00:39:14.900 --> 00:39:16.900 align:middle line:84%
And your hard work
and your diligence

00:39:16.900 --> 00:39:19.480 align:middle line:84%
and your research
and your curiosity,

00:39:19.480 --> 00:39:21.010 align:middle line:84%
combined with your
knowledge of all

00:39:21.010 --> 00:39:22.750 align:middle line:90%
of these great creativities--

00:39:22.750 --> 00:39:25.340 align:middle line:84%
and you're interested in the
hidden truths and the esoteric

00:39:25.340 --> 00:39:27.770 align:middle line:90%
and what's beyond beyond.

00:39:27.770 --> 00:39:28.570 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: Right.

00:39:28.570 --> 00:39:31.210 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: This is the
soup of who you are.

00:39:31.210 --> 00:39:32.440 align:middle line:90%
I think it's fascinating.

00:39:32.440 --> 00:39:34.648 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: I mean I'm
curious about a lot of things.

00:39:34.648 --> 00:39:38.180 align:middle line:84%
And there's still a lot to do,
because I see people becoming--

00:39:38.180 --> 00:39:43.690 align:middle line:84%
what really pains me is to see
people becoming so increasingly

00:39:43.690 --> 00:39:46.790 align:middle line:84%
distracted where I know
they're not listening anymore.

00:39:46.790 --> 00:39:49.060 align:middle line:84%
People are just brain
dead walking out

00:39:49.060 --> 00:39:51.250 align:middle line:90%
in front of cars on the road.

00:39:51.250 --> 00:39:52.810 align:middle line:90%
It's scary in California.

00:39:52.810 --> 00:39:56.650 align:middle line:84%
I don't drive like I used to
because I don't know who's

00:39:56.650 --> 00:39:59.980 align:middle line:84%
going to pull some really
stupid move at the next second,

00:39:59.980 --> 00:40:01.600 align:middle line:90%
because it happens everyday.

00:40:01.600 --> 00:40:03.820 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I've watched some
horrendous crashes lately,

00:40:03.820 --> 00:40:05.330 align:middle line:90%
just horrendous car wrecks.

00:40:05.330 --> 00:40:10.580 align:middle line:84%
And I witnessed a motorcyclist
right where that wall is.

00:40:10.580 --> 00:40:12.550 align:middle line:90%
Don't know what he was thinking.

00:40:12.550 --> 00:40:15.140 align:middle line:84%
Jamming up between the
cars, which is legal,

00:40:15.140 --> 00:40:17.120 align:middle line:90%
going way too fast.

00:40:17.120 --> 00:40:18.700 align:middle line:90%
He didn't apply the brake.

00:40:18.700 --> 00:40:21.500 align:middle line:84%
He just slammed into
the back of a car.

00:40:21.500 --> 00:40:23.910 align:middle line:90%
His motorcycle shattered.

00:40:23.910 --> 00:40:25.630 align:middle line:90%
He went flying through the air.

00:40:25.630 --> 00:40:26.430 align:middle line:90%
Everything.

00:40:26.430 --> 00:40:29.740 align:middle line:84%
And I thought why
didn't he brake?

00:40:29.740 --> 00:40:30.870 align:middle line:90%
What was he thinking?

00:40:30.870 --> 00:40:33.820 align:middle line:84%
And I'm seeing this
stuff all the time now.

00:40:33.820 --> 00:40:36.690 align:middle line:84%
People are not occupying
their bodies anymore.

00:40:36.690 --> 00:40:38.340 align:middle line:84%
They're living on
total distraction.

00:40:38.340 --> 00:40:41.400 align:middle line:84%
And of course, we know that
these devices are largely

00:40:41.400 --> 00:40:42.690 align:middle line:90%
contributing factors.

00:40:42.690 --> 00:40:44.160 align:middle line:90%
He wasn't on a cell phone.

00:40:44.160 --> 00:40:44.550 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: No.

00:40:44.550 --> 00:40:46.091 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: He just
wasn't dialed in.

00:40:46.091 --> 00:40:48.529 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what happened
in his perceptive field.

00:40:48.529 --> 00:40:50.320 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Well, that's
a great point, though,

00:40:50.320 --> 00:40:52.625 align:middle line:84%
about distractibility,
not just with the device,

00:40:52.625 --> 00:40:54.000 align:middle line:84%
because everything
we have access

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:56.050 align:middle line:90%
to with the palm of our hand.

00:40:56.050 --> 00:41:00.930 align:middle line:84%
But it's these other I would
say energies, dimensions,

00:41:00.930 --> 00:41:04.380 align:middle line:84%
whatever you want to call
them are getting louder.

00:41:04.380 --> 00:41:05.400 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: That, too.

00:41:05.400 --> 00:41:10.480 align:middle line:84%
We have this time
now where humanity

00:41:10.480 --> 00:41:13.630 align:middle line:84%
and the other dimensions
are closer to one another.

00:41:13.630 --> 00:41:17.670 align:middle line:84%
But what a lot of people
in the metaphysical field

00:41:17.670 --> 00:41:20.100 align:middle line:84%
don't bring up or
don't understand

00:41:20.100 --> 00:41:22.500 align:middle line:90%
is it goes both ways.

00:41:22.500 --> 00:41:24.960 align:middle line:84%
You have higher
frequency beings that

00:41:24.960 --> 00:41:27.720 align:middle line:84%
are more readily
available, that are there

00:41:27.720 --> 00:41:31.170 align:middle line:84%
to guide you and protect you
and work with you until you can

00:41:31.170 --> 00:41:33.540 align:middle line:84%
remember and do
it yourself, which

00:41:33.540 --> 00:41:36.249 align:middle line:84%
could take us a very long time
to get back to that place.

00:41:36.249 --> 00:41:37.290 align:middle line:90%
But they're there for us.

00:41:37.290 --> 00:41:38.610 align:middle line:90%
And everybody has them.

00:41:38.610 --> 00:41:40.950 align:middle line:84%
They're benevolent beings
who have given-- they're

00:41:40.950 --> 00:41:42.780 align:middle line:90%
giving their service to us.

00:41:42.780 --> 00:41:44.160 align:middle line:90%
And we can tap in at any time.

00:41:44.160 --> 00:41:45.600 align:middle line:84%
And we know the
wonderful stories

00:41:45.600 --> 00:41:49.770 align:middle line:84%
of kind of angelic experiences
that happen at car crash sites

00:41:49.770 --> 00:41:52.530 align:middle line:84%
where someone seems to have
just been gently lifted

00:41:52.530 --> 00:41:54.480 align:middle line:84%
and they're 20 feet
from their car, safe,

00:41:54.480 --> 00:41:55.890 align:middle line:90%
without a broken bone.

00:41:55.890 --> 00:41:56.910 align:middle line:90%
They do that.

00:41:56.910 --> 00:41:58.620 align:middle line:84%
On the other hand,
if you're looking

00:41:58.620 --> 00:42:01.740 align:middle line:84%
at the Earth is sandwiched
between higher realms and lower

00:42:01.740 --> 00:42:05.430 align:middle line:84%
realms, the lower realm beings
are much more in touch, too.

00:42:05.430 --> 00:42:07.290 align:middle line:84%
And if you have taken
your frequencies

00:42:07.290 --> 00:42:12.840 align:middle line:84%
down to points of resentment,
anger, hatred, lack

00:42:12.840 --> 00:42:16.302 align:middle line:84%
of compassion, and
so forth, you're

00:42:16.302 --> 00:42:17.760 align:middle line:84%
a great companion
for these beings.

00:42:17.760 --> 00:42:18.930 align:middle line:90%
They can come right in.

00:42:18.930 --> 00:42:22.370 align:middle line:84%
And so now you're being
infected kind of the wrong way,

00:42:22.370 --> 00:42:23.820 align:middle line:90%
the downward way.

00:42:23.820 --> 00:42:26.280 align:middle line:84%
And it's going to take
time and a lot of will

00:42:26.280 --> 00:42:28.320 align:middle line:84%
to pull yourself
back up out of that.

00:42:28.320 --> 00:42:31.930 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Well, we have
this polarized world--

00:42:31.930 --> 00:42:32.730 align:middle line:90%
>>MEREDITH: Yes.

00:42:32.730 --> 00:42:34.271 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --right now
that is very much

00:42:34.271 --> 00:42:38.340 align:middle line:84%
a battle between those lower
frequencies, the competition,

00:42:38.340 --> 00:42:42.067 align:middle line:84%
the lies, and those higher
frequencies, those that see

00:42:42.067 --> 00:42:42.900 align:middle line:90%
hope for the future.

00:42:42.900 --> 00:42:45.570 align:middle line:84%
And I feel as humanity,
we are sandwiched right

00:42:45.570 --> 00:42:47.917 align:middle line:84%
where we could make
it either decision.

00:42:47.917 --> 00:42:49.500 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: You can
choose your world.

00:42:49.500 --> 00:42:50.410 align:middle line:90%
Everybody has the right.

00:42:50.410 --> 00:42:52.910 align:middle line:84%
If you want to stay in anger
and resentment about things you

00:42:52.910 --> 00:42:56.810 align:middle line:84%
literally cannot
control, then stay angry.

00:42:56.810 --> 00:42:57.999 align:middle line:90%
Stay resentful.

00:42:57.999 --> 00:42:59.790 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And that's what
you'll get more of.

00:42:59.790 --> 00:43:01.110 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: That's what
you're going to get more of.

00:43:01.110 --> 00:43:02.247 align:middle line:90%
But that's a choice.

00:43:02.247 --> 00:43:03.330 align:middle line:90%
That's an absolute choice.

00:43:03.330 --> 00:43:07.260 align:middle line:84%
Now it feels like I can't
believe that tweet that

00:43:07.260 --> 00:43:08.250 align:middle line:90%
came out this morning.

00:43:08.250 --> 00:43:11.430 align:middle line:84%
And you could just be beside
yourself with frustration

00:43:11.430 --> 00:43:13.230 align:middle line:84%
and, you know, upset
and everything.

00:43:13.230 --> 00:43:14.520 align:middle line:90%
But you can't stay there.

00:43:14.520 --> 00:43:16.450 align:middle line:84%
You've got to let
it go and get back

00:43:16.450 --> 00:43:20.140 align:middle line:84%
into what you can produce
with your own time on Earth

00:43:20.140 --> 00:43:21.720 align:middle line:90%
with your own energy.

00:43:21.720 --> 00:43:25.500 align:middle line:84%
And keep yourself moving in
that direction if you can.

00:43:25.500 --> 00:43:27.800 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: There's so many
questions that I have for you.

00:43:27.800 --> 00:43:31.230 align:middle line:84%
And I want to learn more
about whisperings of the soul.

00:43:31.230 --> 00:43:33.780 align:middle line:84%
Could you share that
with us a little bit?

00:43:33.780 --> 00:43:35.670 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: The soul
and the soul higher

00:43:35.670 --> 00:43:37.440 align:middle line:84%
mind complex, they
work together.

00:43:37.440 --> 00:43:39.420 align:middle line:84%
If you're looking at it
through hermetic terms,

00:43:39.420 --> 00:43:42.690 align:middle line:84%
the soul would be the
positive and the higher mind

00:43:42.690 --> 00:43:44.037 align:middle line:90%
would be the negative.

00:43:44.037 --> 00:43:45.120 align:middle line:90%
And that doesn't mean bad.

00:43:45.120 --> 00:43:47.790 align:middle line:84%
It means positive and
negative are paired together

00:43:47.790 --> 00:43:49.350 align:middle line:90%
of the soul complex.

00:43:49.350 --> 00:43:52.110 align:middle line:84%
The higher mind is the part
that is talking to you.

00:43:52.110 --> 00:43:55.590 align:middle line:84%
The soul is what
incarnates along

00:43:55.590 --> 00:43:59.700 align:middle line:84%
with the higher mind, along
with the subconscious.

00:43:59.700 --> 00:44:03.600 align:middle line:84%
All the information from
before comes with you.

00:44:03.600 --> 00:44:06.960 align:middle line:84%
It's hidden in there in the
subconscious, subconscious.

00:44:06.960 --> 00:44:11.310 align:middle line:84%
So when you have a sudden
fear of, for example, heights,

00:44:11.310 --> 00:44:13.560 align:middle line:84%
you've probably brought that
through from another time

00:44:13.560 --> 00:44:14.940 align:middle line:84%
if you haven't had any
negative experience.

00:44:14.940 --> 00:44:15.390 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right, right.

00:44:15.390 --> 00:44:17.973 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: So that's the kind
of subconscious doing its thing

00:44:17.973 --> 00:44:18.780 align:middle line:90%
to protect you.

00:44:18.780 --> 00:44:21.210 align:middle line:84%
The higher mind is in connection
with the soul directly.

00:44:21.210 --> 00:44:24.570 align:middle line:84%
And it's, like, no,
this person, you

00:44:24.570 --> 00:44:27.360 align:middle line:84%
need to be patient with this
person in your life now,

00:44:27.360 --> 00:44:30.300 align:middle line:84%
because maybe this is a person
that you harmed in another time

00:44:30.300 --> 00:44:32.430 align:middle line:90%
or dismissed or something.

00:44:32.430 --> 00:44:34.710 align:middle line:84%
And I'm giving really
baby examples of it.

00:44:34.710 --> 00:44:37.200 align:middle line:84%
And so the soul's whispering
through the higher mind, which

00:44:37.200 --> 00:44:39.420 align:middle line:84%
is whispering down to
your everyday mind,

00:44:39.420 --> 00:44:41.190 align:middle line:90%
your conscious mind.

00:44:41.190 --> 00:44:43.590 align:middle line:84%
No, you get this
little feeling, it's

00:44:43.590 --> 00:44:46.080 align:middle line:84%
going to be such a bitch
with this person right now.

00:44:46.080 --> 00:44:47.760 align:middle line:90%
And I feel so bad about it.

00:44:47.760 --> 00:44:50.010 align:middle line:90%
I should be more patient.

00:44:50.010 --> 00:44:51.900 align:middle line:84%
That's actually the
higher mind interpreting

00:44:51.900 --> 00:44:54.510 align:middle line:84%
a whispering coming
through, that this needs

00:44:54.510 --> 00:44:55.860 align:middle line:90%
to be balanced and adjusted.

00:44:55.860 --> 00:44:56.690 align:middle line:90%
So pay attention.

00:44:56.690 --> 00:44:57.940 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It does take slowing--

00:44:57.940 --> 00:44:59.898 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: You dredge
up something in yourself

00:44:59.898 --> 00:45:01.350 align:middle line:90%
that can do this better.

00:45:01.350 --> 00:45:03.660 align:middle line:84%
And that's the higher
mind speaking to you.

00:45:03.660 --> 00:45:06.720 align:middle line:84%
