though, to hear those messages.

00:45:06.720 --> 00:45:07.850 align:middle line:84%
>>MEREDITH: And we're
not slowing down.

00:45:07.850 --> 00:45:08.490 align:middle line:90%
We're speeding up.

00:45:08.490 --> 00:45:09.280 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: As we talked about
a little bit earlier.

